# .qa-shared — list non-tracked files to mount read-only into QA containers
# Paths are relative to your project root (APP_ROOT).
# Lines starting with # are comments; blank lines are ignored.
#
# fleet init auto-populates this file with an idempotent marker block that
# lists .env files it discovers in APP_ROOT, FRONTEND_DIR, and BACKEND_DIR.
# Re-running fleet init replaces only the block contents without touching any
# lines you add outside the markers.
#
# You can add further entries outside the auto-discovered block — for example:
# d2r2-frontend/.npmrc
# d2r2-backend/.env
# .env
